[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0009","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0199","title":"GNU glibc 未加检查的返回值漏洞","description":"GNU C 库（glibc）2.2 之前版本的 tdelete 函数在删除树根节点时未明确说明返回值类型，导致开发者无法正确判断操作结果，从而可能访问悬空指针。攻击者可利用此缺陷绕过安全检查或触发程序崩溃，影响所有依赖 glibc 的 Linux 系统及应用。该漏洞源于对返回值未加检查（CWE-252），CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0199"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2020-10-06T13:15:13.087","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.723","remediation":"升级 GNU C Library (glibc) 至 2.2 及以上版本，该版本已明确定义 tdelete 函数在删除树根节点时的返回值。开发者应在调用 tdelete 后始终检查返回值是否为 NULL，避免使用悬空指针。无法立即升级的应用可通过静态代码扫描工具（如 cppcheck）检测 tdelete 返回值未检查的模式。临时缓解措施可结合内存安全防护机制（如 AddressSanitizer）在开发阶段捕获此类缺陷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/glibc/glibc-2.2.tar.gz","https://github.com/bminor/glibc/commit/2864e767053317538feafa815046fff89e5a16be#diff-94e8c502f255fdfc346df0e29fd4ef40","https://www.cee.studio/tdelete.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1090","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1090.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1374","title":"perlshop.cgi 购物车程序敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"perlshop.cgi 购物车程序存在敏感信息泄露漏洞，该程序将客户订单信息、信用卡号等敏感数据以文件形式存储在 Web 根目录下，未进行任何访问控制。远程攻击者只需通过 HTTP 请求直接访问这些文件路径即可获取客户敏感信息，导致用户隐私数据泄露。该漏洞影响使用 perlshop.cgi 的早期 Perl 购物车系统，攻击条件简单，无需身份认证。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1374"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2005-05-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:18.230","remediation":"立即将 perlshop.cgi 的数据存储目录移出 Web 根目录（如移至 /var/lib/perlshop/），并在 Web 服务器配置中禁止直接访问该目录（Apache 使用 <Directory> 指令或 .htaccess 的 Deny from all）。由于 perlshop.cgi 已长期无人维护，建议迁移至现代购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce）并删除旧脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92523159819402&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1090.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1090.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1090.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1104","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1104.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1431","title":"Microsoft Zero Administration Kit (ZAK) 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Zero Administration Kit (ZAK) 1.0 的 Appstation 模式存在安全策略绕过漏洞。本地用户可通过 Office 97 应用程序（如 Word）启动资源管理器，将恶意软件安装至 TEMP 目录，并将其重命名为允许运行的程序名称（如 Winword.exe），从而绕过\"仅允许运行指定应用程序\"策略限制，实现非授权软件执行。该漏洞影响 ZAK 1.0 及 Office97 环境，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危，攻击者需具备本地访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1431"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2005-01-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:25.593","remediation":"该漏洞存在于已停止支持的 ZAK 1.0 和 Office 97 中，建议升级到受支持的 Windows 环境（如 Windows 10/11 企业版）并使用组策略或 MDM 方案替代 ZAK 实现应用程序白名单控制。若无法升级，可通过修改注册表禁用 Office 应用中的 VBA 和 Shell 调用权限，并移除 TEMP 目录的可执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91576100022688&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91606260910008&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/181","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19144"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1104.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1089","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1089.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1373","title":"FORE PowerHub 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FORE PowerHub 5.0.0 及更早版本存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 nmap 等工具发送特制的 TCP SYN 扫描包并结合 TCP/IP 操作系统指纹探测技术，导致目标设备响应异常并陷入挂起状态，无法正常提供服务。该漏洞影响 PowerHub 5.0.0 及之前版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1373"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2005-01-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:18.090","remediation":"升级 FORE PowerHub 至 5.0.1 或更高版本以修复该拒绝服务漏洞。如无法升级，可在网络边界防火墙配置规则，限制对 PowerHub 管理端口的 SYN 扫描探测，或部署入侵检测系统拦截 nmap 等扫描工具的特征流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91651770130771&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1089.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1028","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1028.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1263","title":"Metamail Metamail 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Metamail 2.7-7.2 之前版本在处理邮件附件时存在任意文件写入漏洞。其 sun-audio-file 等脚本会调用 uuencode 解码附件，而解码过程未对附件头中指定的目标路径做限制，导致攻击者可构造一封包含 uuencoded 附件的电子邮件，在附件中指定任意文件的完整路径名。当受害者使用存在漏洞的 Metamail 查看该邮件时，系统会按攻击者指定的路径将解码内容写入目标文件，从而覆盖或创建任意文件。该漏洞无需身份认证，仅需向目标用户发送特制邮件且其在客户端中打开即可触发，攻击者可借此篡改敏感文件、植入恶意内容或破坏系统稳定性，影响范围涵盖所有使用受影响版本 Metamail 处理邮件的 Unix/Linux 系统用户。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1263"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2003-08-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.937","remediation":"升级 Metamail 至 2.7-7.2 及以上版本（如 Debian 安装 metamail_2.7-7.2 或后续发行包），从源头修复 uuencode 脚本未校验路径的问题。如暂无法升级，可在邮件网关或 MTA 上禁用 uuencode 附件解码、过滤包含完整路径名的 uuencoded 附件，并限制 metamail 运行账户的写权限，避免其可写入系统关键目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87773365324657&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1677","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1263.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1263","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1263.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1263.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xqm9-g4jx-xvgw/GHSA-xqm9-g4jx-xvgw.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1263.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_147200_147300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--994159c6-4130-4132-93c9-332283f85f73.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--994159c6-4130-4132-93c9-332283f85f73.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1028.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0926","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0926.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1081","title":"Novell Netware Web Server files.pl 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare Web 服务器 3.x 自带的 files.pl CGI 脚本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求，利用 `../../` 等目录穿越序列绕过访问限制，读取服务器上任意文件（如 `/etc/passwd` 等敏感配置文件）。该漏洞影响 Novell WebServer Examples Toolkit 2 及 NetWare Web Server 3.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。Novell 官方未发布正式补丁，建议禁用或删除不必要的 CGI 脚本以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1081"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2002-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.900","remediation":"删除 Web 服务器上的 `files.pl` 脚本文件，或通过 Web 服务器配置限制对 CGI 目录的访问（如禁止执行未授权的 .pl 脚本）。升级到 Novell NetWare 5.1 及以上版本可彻底规避该问题，也可在 Web 服务器层面配置 URL 过滤规则阻止对 `files.pl` 的访问请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.roxanne.org/faqs/www-secure/wwwsf4.html#Q35","http://www.w3.org/Security/Faq/wwwsf8.html#Q87","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2054","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20482","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1081.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1081","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1081.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1081.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1081.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-487h-5pmw-j735/GHSA-487h-5pmw-j735.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88445/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1081.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0926.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0934","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0934.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1091","title":"tin和rtin UNIX新闻阅读器符号链接漏洞","description":"UNIX 系统下的新闻阅读器 tin 和 rtin 以不安全权限创建临时文件 /tmp/.tin_log，且程序会跟随符号链接进行操作。本地攻击者可通过符号链接攻击，将 /tmp/.tin_log 指向目标文件，从而修改当前用户具有写入权限的其他文件权限，导致本地权限提升或敏感文件被篡改。该漏洞影响各类 UNIX 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议避免使用存在此问题的 tin/rtin 版本，或手动修正临时文件权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1091"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2002-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.177","remediation":"升级 tin/rtin 至 1.5 以上版本，新版本使用 mkstemp() 安全创建临时文件，避免符号链接竞争。如无法升级，在脚本中创建 /tmp/.tin_log 前手动检查并删除已有符号链接，或设置 umask 077 限制文件权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419835&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419839&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420726&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/431","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1091","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1091.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/SAP/fosstars-rating-core/blob/7b172f42f218f6cfad42f81bd9c9ef49de35b919/docs/oss/security/google/tink.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_148200_148300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2eb5fb46-4192-4cdd-9ec8-81213bad695e.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--2eb5fb46-4192-4cdd-9ec8-81213bad695e.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0934.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0998","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0998.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1174","title":"Iomega ZIP-100 磁盘驱动器密码保护绕过漏洞","description":"Iomega ZIP-100 磁盘驱动器存在密码保护绕过漏洞，具有物理访问权限的攻击者可利用该漏洞绕过磁盘密码保护。攻击方式为：先插入已知密码的磁盘，等待驱动器断电后手动替换为目标磁盘，再用已知密码访问受保护的目标磁盘中的数据。该漏洞影响 Iomega ZIP-100 系列驱动器，需要物理接触目标设备，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1174"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-12-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.640","remediation":"由于该漏洞为 Iomega ZIP-100 硬件设计缺陷，官方已停止支持且无固件补丁。建议立即停止在涉密场景使用 ZIP-100 驱动器，改用支持硬件加密的现代存储设备；如继续使用，须对所有数据在写入前使用第三方加密软件（如 VeraCrypt、BitLocker）进行全盘加密，并确保驱动器物理存放于上锁机柜或受限访问区域，防止未经授权的人员接触。作为临时缓解措施，在驱动器使用完毕后彻底断开电源并移除数据线。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.counterpane.com/crypto-gram-9812.html#doghouse"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0998.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0877","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0877.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1024","title":"LBL Tcpdump 3.4 ip_print 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"tcpdump 3.4a 及更早版本中的 ip_print 函数存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的零长度头部数据包，当 tcpdump 解析并打印该数据包时，会触发无限循环导致核心转储，从而使服务崩溃。该漏洞影响运行 tcpdump 3.4a 的系统，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1024"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-11-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.747","remediation":"升级到 tcpdump 3.4a7 及以上版本，该版本已移除导致死循环的递归 ip_print 调用。临时缓解措施：使用 tcpdump -s 24 限制抓包长度，或在内核层面添加 iptables 规则丢弃协议 4（IPIP）的异常报文。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92955903802773&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92963447601748&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92989907627051&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/313","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19251","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1024","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1024.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4xf9-whrj-cqwc/GHSA-4xf9-whrj-cqwc.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/313/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_151700_151800.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a2475725-573a-44a3-9fee-e5b8ed92fad2.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0877.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1144","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1144.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1514","title":"Celtech ExpressFS FTP 服务器远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ExpressFS FTP 服务器 2.x 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当攻击者向 FTP 服务的 USER 命令发送超长字符串时，可触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致 FTP 服务进程崩溃造成拒绝服务，在特定条件下可进一步实现远程代码执行。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用该漏洞，只需网络可达目标 FTP 端口（默认 21）即可发起攻击。该漏洞影响 Celtech ExpressFS FTP 服务器 2.x 全版本，危害等级高，建议用户尽快升级至修复版本或迁移至其他受支持的 FTP 服务软件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1514"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-11-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:36.223","remediation":"ExpressFS FTP Server 2.x 厂商已停止支持且无安全补丁发布，最彻底的修复措施是停止使用该产品，迁移至主动维护的 FTP 服务器如 vsftpd 或 FileZilla Server。临时缓解措施可在防火墙层面限制对 FTP 端口（21/TCP）的访问来源 IP，仅允许可信主机连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94121377716133&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94130292519646&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/749","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3401","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1514.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1514","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1514.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1514.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce70cbcf8165046f2229cbe0d9f53c47bf63ece0/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-87hw-jg6c-ggf2/GHSA-87hw-jg6c-ggf2.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/749/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_151700_151800.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1514.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7ab4292b-6860-4a16-8474-66e7c991e0ac.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8200d63179d89b9076027cd96356d55ef8a5349e/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1144.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0025","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0025.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0359","title":"Marc Schaefer ptylogin 拒绝服务及密码泄露漏洞","description":"Unix 系统中的 ptylogin 工具存在访问控制缺陷，本地用户可通过操纵伪终端设备锁定调制解调器，导致合法用户无法拨入（拒绝服务）；亦可利用该缺陷以调制解调器身份向外拨号，或截获拨入用户的登录密码。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，影响所有使用 ptylogin 管理串行拨号会话的 Unix 系统，攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限即可实施攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0359"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.617","remediation":"立即升级 ptylogin 至最新安全版本；同时移除 ptylogin 二进制文件的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/ptylogin），并将可执行权限限制为仅授权用户组。对调制解调器设备文件（/dev/ttyS*、/dev/modem）设置 600 权限，仅允许 root 和拨号用户组访问。实施回拨认证机制作为临时缓解措施，并建议用 SSH 或 VPN 替代基于调制解调器的远程接入方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0359","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0359","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0359.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vwjf-9p53-995f/GHSA-vwjf-9p53-995f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82482/info.html","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0025.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0234","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0234.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0681","title":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server (PWS) 1.0 的服务器扩展组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送超长 URL 请求，触发缓冲区溢出，导致 Web 服务崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 平台上的 FrontPage 服务器扩展 3.0.2.926 及可能其他版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，但仅能导致服务异常终止，无法实现代码执行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0681"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.150","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 Windows 95 及 Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 1.0（Server Extensions 3.0.2.926）。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并部署 IIS 或 Apache 等现代 Web 服务器。无法升级时，可部署 WAF/IPS 设备过滤超长 URL 请求，限制 URL 长度不超过 2048 字节，并在防火墙层面限制对 PWS 服务的访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1999-q3/0381.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/568","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3117","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19445"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0234.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0234.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0234.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0324","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0324.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0729","title":"IBM Lotus Notes LDAP 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lotus Notes 的 LDAP 服务（NLDAP）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 ldap_search 请求触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Lotus Domino Server 及 Lotus Notes 相关版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。攻击者可通过网络远程利用，攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0729"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.097","remediation":"升级 IBM Lotus Domino 至 R5.0.1 及以上版本，该版本已修复 NLDAP 服务中 ldap_search 请求的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，可在防火墙或网络层面限制对 LDAP 端口（默认 389）的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 连接，以降低被远程利用的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-061.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/1057","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/601","http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise34.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0729.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0729","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0729.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0729.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q9vv-w9pw-fj27/GHSA-q9vv-w9pw-fj27.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_150600_150700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0729.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0324.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0474","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0474.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0758","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server 源代码泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1 及 FastTrack 3.01 版本存在源代码泄露漏洞。远程攻击者通过在脚本 URL 后附加 %20（URL 编码的空格字符），可绕过服务器对脚本文件的访问限制，直接查看服务器端脚本的源代码。该漏洞导致敏感业务逻辑、数据库连接信息等泄露，为后续攻击提供便利。攻击无需认证，仅需构造特制 URL 即可触发，利用难度低。受影响版本包括 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1 和 FastTrack 3.01。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0758"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.743","remediation":"升级 Netscape Enterprise Server 至 3.6 及以上版本，或升级 FastTrack 至 4.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，在服务器配置中禁用脚本源码泄露功能，并配置 Web 服务器仅解析 .cgi/.pl 等脚本扩展名，拒绝直接访问脚本文件。长期建议迁移至 Apache 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0758","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0758.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0758","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0758.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0758.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-95vm-hxfq-7rhx/GHSA-95vm-hxfq-7rhx.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0758.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0758.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e4ccecb3-d057-4a20-8cdc-28689290f87a.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0474.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0513","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0513.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0784","title":"Oracle Database Server TNSLSNR SQL*Net Listener 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Oracle TNSLSNR SQL*Net Listener 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向监听端口发送特制的畸形字符串，导致监听服务崩溃或停止响应，从而阻断合法数据库连接。该漏洞影响 Oracle Database Server 7.1.4 及 7.3.3 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。Oracle 官方已发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0784"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.073","remediation":"升级 Oracle Database Server 至 8.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在 listener.ora 中设置 ADMIN_RESTRICTIONS_LISTENER=ON 并配置监听器密码，同时在防火墙层面限制对 1521 端口的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1998_4/0764.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1999_1/0056.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/1998/msg00536.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0513.toml"}]